<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="catalog_script_client"><catalog_script_client action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><applies_catalog>true</applies_catalog><applies_extended>false</applies_extended><applies_req_item>false</applies_req_item><applies_sc_task>false</applies_sc_task><applies_target_record>false</applies_target_record><applies_to>item</applies_to><cat_item display_value="Car parking reservation">f64205c54709711021f49128436d433a</cat_item><cat_variable>IO:8413ec754701711021f49128436d4328</cat_variable><condition/><description/><field/><global>true</global><isolate_script>true</isolate_script><messages/><name>Submit ที่จอดซ้ำ วันเวลาเดียวกัน</name><order/><script><![CDATA[function onSubmit() {
    //Type appropriate comment here, and begin script below

    var id_card = g_form.getValue('u_id_card');
    var num_car = g_form.getValue('u_number_car');
    var location = g_form.getValue('u_location');
    var start = g_form.getValue('u_start_dt');
    var end = g_form.getValue('u_end_dt');
	
    var call = new GlideAjax('Check_location');
    call.addParam('sysparm_name', 'query_location');
    call.addParam('id', id_card);
    call.addParam('num_car', num_car);
    call.addParam('location', location);
    call.addParam('st', start);
    call.addParam('end', end);

    call.getXML(getResponse);
	
    function getResponse(response) {
        var result = response.responseXML.documentElement.getAttribute('answer');
        alert(result);
        if (result != null) {
            g_form.setValue('u_confirm', false);
        }
    }

	return false;   

}]]></script><sys_class_name>catalog_script_client</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2023-09-05 14:59:53</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>f99e76524709f11021f49128436d438f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>46</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Submit ที่จอดซ้ำ วันเวลาเดียวกัน</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Car parking reservation" source="x_950909_car_park">083c1ad84741311021f49128436d4349</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Car parking reservation">083c1ad84741311021f49128436d4349</sys_scope><sys_update_name>catalog_script_client_f99e76524709f11021f49128436d438f</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2023-09-06 12:13:24</sys_updated_on><table/><type>onSubmit</type><ui_type>10</ui_type><variable_set/><view/></catalog_script_client></record_update>
